Given the following program and the first line of a loop, optimize it out via loop unrolling.. The program is 
typedef long a;
fn1() {}
typedef a d __attribute__((__vector_size__(sizeof(a))));
d fn2() { return (d){fn1}; }
main() {
  int xxx = 0;
  while (xxx < 10) {
    xxx++;
    // loop body
  }
}
.                 The target to be optimized is while (xxx) { ... }.
